#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.53"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.53:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.53:0.2"
msgid "6. Gotamīvagga"
msgstr "6. Gotamī"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 53. Saṅkhittasutta → saṅkhittagotamiyovādasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.53:0.3"
msgid "53. Saṅkhittasutta"
msgstr "53. Brief Advice to Gotamī"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.53:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Vesālī, at the Great Wood, in the "
"hall with the peaked roof."

msgctxt "an8.53:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho mahāpajāpatī gotamī yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā "
"mahāpajāpatī gotamī bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Mahāpajāpatī Gotamī went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, "
"and said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.53:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena dhammaṃ desetu, yamahaṃ bhagavato "
"dhammaṃ sutvā ekā vūpakaṭṭhā appamattā ātāpinī pahitattā vihareyyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’"
"ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.”"

msgctxt "an8.53:2.2"
msgid "“Ye kho tvaṃ, gotami, dhamme jāneyyāsi:"
msgstr "“Gotamī, you might know that certain things"

msgctxt "an8.53:2.3"
msgid "‘ime dhammā sarāgāya saṃvattanti, no virāgāya;"
msgstr "lead to passion, not dispassion;"

msgctxt "an8.53:2.4"
msgid "saṃyogāya saṃvattanti, no visaṃyogāya;"
msgstr "to being fettered, not to being unfettered;"

msgctxt "an8.53:2.5"
msgid "ācayāya saṃvattanti, no apacayāya;"
msgstr "to accumulation, not dispersal;"

msgctxt "an8.53:2.6"
msgid "mahicchatāya saṃvattanti, no appicchatāya;"
msgstr "to more desires, not fewer;"

msgctxt "an8.53:2.7"
msgid "asantuṭṭhiyā saṃvattanti, no santuṭṭhiyā;"
msgstr "to discontentment, not contentment;"

msgctxt "an8.53:2.8"
msgid "saṅgaṇikāya saṃvattanti, no pavivekāya;"
msgstr "to crowding, not seclusion;"

msgctxt "an8.53:2.9"
msgid "kosajjāya saṃvattanti, no vīriyārambhāya;"
msgstr "to laziness, not energy;"

msgctxt "an8.53:2.10"
msgid "dubbharatāya saṃvattanti, no subharatāyā’ti, "
msgstr "to being hard to look after, not being easy to look after. "

msgctxt "an8.53:2.11"
msgid "ekaṃsena, gotami, dhāreyyāsi:"
msgstr "You should definitely bear in mind that these things are"

msgctxt "an8.53:2.12"
msgid "‘neso dhammo, neso vinayo, netaṃ satthusāsanan’ti."
msgstr "not the teaching, not the training, and not the Teacher’s instructions."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.281"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.53:3.1"
msgid "Ye ca kho tvaṃ, gotami, dhamme jāneyyāsi:"
msgstr "You might know that certain things"

msgctxt "an8.53:3.2"
msgid "‘ime dhammā virāgāya saṃvattanti, no sarāgāya;"
msgstr "lead to dispassion, not passion;"

msgctxt "an8.53:3.3"
msgid "visaṃyogāya saṃvattanti, no saṃyogāya;"
msgstr "to being unfettered, not to being fettered;"

msgctxt "an8.53:3.4"
msgid "apacayāya saṃvattanti, no ācayāya;"
msgstr "to dispersal, not accumulation;"

msgctxt "an8.53:3.5"
msgid "appicchatāya saṃvattanti, no mahicchatāya;"
msgstr "to fewer desires, not more;"

msgctxt "an8.53:3.6"
msgid "santuṭṭhiyā saṃvattanti, no asantuṭṭhiyā;"
msgstr "to contentment, not discontentment;"

msgctxt "an8.53:3.7"
msgid "pavivekāya saṃvattanti, no saṅgaṇikāya;"
msgstr "to seclusion, not crowding;"

msgctxt "an8.53:3.8"
msgid "vīriyārambhāya saṃvattanti, no kosajjāya;"
msgstr "to energy, not laziness;"

msgctxt "an8.53:3.9"
msgid "subharatāya saṃvattanti, no dubbharatāyā’ti, "
msgstr "to being easy to look after, not being hard to look after. "

msgctxt "an8.53:3.10"
msgid "ekaṃsena, gotami, dhāreyyāsi:"
msgstr "You should definitely bear in mind that these things are"

msgctxt "an8.53:3.11"
msgid "‘eso dhammo, eso vinayo, etaṃ satthusāsanan’”ti."
msgstr "the teaching, the training, and the Teacher’s instructions.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.53:3.12"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
